Hancock LEE

ABT 1750 - ____

ID Number: I37767

OCCUPATION: Clerk of Essex Co. VA until 1792

RESIDENCE: Westmoreland Co. VA

BIRTH: ABT 1750

RESOURCES: See: [S965] [S2095] [S2874]

Father: John LEE of Maryland

Mother: Susannah SMITH

Family 1 : Ann SMITH

Notes

His will makes no mention of children. Hancock succeeded his father as Clerk of Essex Co., and held the position until 1792, when he was succeeded by his brother, Philip Ludwell, who continued in office until 1814.
